title: Service Agreement — Dalil Technology and Acme Corporation
summary: Fixed-term platform development agreement, sealed and tamper-evident.

meta: | author: Legal | type: contract

section: Parties
text: **Dalil Technology LLC**, registered in Doha, Qatar ("Provider")
text: **Acme Corporation**, registered in Doha, Qatar ("Client")

section: 1. Scope
text: The Provider shall design, build, and maintain the Client document platform as described in Schedule A.

section: 2. Term
text: This agreement runs from 2026-07-01 to 2027-06-30 unless terminated under Section 4.

section: 3. Fees
text: Monthly fee | end: 12,000 QAR
text: Payment terms | end: Net 14 days
deadline: First invoice due | date: 2026-07-15

section: 4. Termination
text: Either party may terminate with 30 days written notice.

